= Introduction =
The Boo Framework is a collection of PHP and jQuery objects joined in a loosely coupled framework designed for rapid application development.

Boo can preform many common tasks including:
  * Page Templates - Including support for [http://code.google.com/p/ramaboo/w/list Smarty].
  * Browser Detection
  * Database Abstraction
  * Error Handling
  * User Management
  * Group Permission
  * System Logging
  * SMS Messaging
  * Data Validation

Boo works with the following services:
  * [http://twitter.com/ Twitter]
  * [http://authorize.net/ Authorize.Net]
  * [http://random.irb.hr/ Quantum Random Bit Generator Service]

Boo can generate any XHTML tag with a simple to use object oriented interface making dynamic site generation a breeze.

Interesting in working with Boo? Check out the [http://code.google.com/p/ramaboo/source/browse/trunk source]. Learn more in the [http://code.google.com/p/ramaboo/w/list Wiki].
